                      p.card-text It is a free and open-source programming language developed and maintained by Microsoft. It is a strict superset of JavaScript, and adds optional static typing and class-based object-oriented programming to the language. TypeScript may be used to develop JavaScript applications for client-side or server-side (Node.js) execution.
                    a.btn.btn-block.btn-primary(href='#') Start Now
                .card
                  .img-wrapper
                    img.card-img-top.img-fluid(
                      src='http://ithub.hu/images/blog/es6.jpg'
