                  .card-block
                    .title-wrapper
                      h4.card-title ECMAScript
                    .description-wrapper
                      p.card-text ECMAScript 6, also known as ECMAScript 2015, is the latest version of the ECMAScript standard. ES6 is a significant update to the language, and the first update to the language since ES5 was standardized in 2009. Implementation of these features in major JavaScript engines is underway now.
                    a.btn.btn-block.btn-primary(href='#') Start Now
